  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">chromatic metal</span>, generated by fusion in the heart of a star.<br><br>Emeril is found on planets orbiting <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">green stars</span>, and can be placed in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> to create purified <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Chromatic Metal</span> for use in the manufacture of advanced technologies.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>在恒星的中心融合产生。<br><br>艾梅里尔可在环绕<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">绿色恒星</span>的行星上发现，可以放在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中制造出纯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>以供生产先进技术使用。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>在恒星的中心融合产生。<br><br>艾梅里尔可在环绕<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">绿色恒星</span>的行星上发现，可以放在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中制造出纯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>以供生产先进技术使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>，恆星中心熔合時生成。<br><br>砪可見於環繞<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">綠色恆星</span>的星球，可放入<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>製成純化<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>，再用來製作先進科技。"
  },
